title: Gen. John Galvin, a NATO Supreme Allied Commander, Dies at 86
text:
Published By: NYTimes US News - Today 
General Galvin oversaw the North Atlantic military alliance from 1987 to 1992, retooling it into a more mobile, flexible multinational force...
